                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000115-62-off361 t18000115-62-cd362"></join>, a cheese, value 15s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t18000115-62-victim540" type="victimName">
                  Joshua 
                  Bewley
               <interp inst="t18000115-62-victim540" type="surname" value="Bewley"></interp>
